data.description: **Motivated seller!  And a brand new roof being completed soon!  This traditional and spacious remodeled townhome is located in a quiet neighborhood, near CISD's Bowie Elementary. You'll fall in love with the layout featuring an entire master wing, large bedrooms all with sizable walk in closets, and a great living area open to the dining room and entertaining space. The kitchen with granite counter tops, double ovens, and a large pantry, also has great cabinet space. The breakfast nook can function as more than just dining as it features two granite desk areas with great built ins, and the adorably unique stained glass window. The atrium with water hookup was created with relaxation in mind featuring a brilliant skylight. No more lawn duties for you, as the HOA takes care of yard maintenance. What's not to love? With modern comfort, modern technology, and ultra convenience, this property has it all. Come see it for yourself!
